Ideas 
Find all companies that offer "above average" paid time off days, maternity leave, average employee tenure, and healthcare benefits
Make a ranking of industries by their revenue from best to worst
How many companies have above average, average, and below average employee tenure?
Employee counts to be recategorized from small, medium, and large?

Find tech jobs that meets these requirements of 1. Having health insurance and 2. PTO of 20 days or more.
  SELECT company_name, industry, healthcare_benefits, paid_time_off_days
  FROM fortune_companies
  WHERE industry = "Technology"
  AND healthcare_benefits = 1
  AND paid_time_off_days >=20;
